sourcesContent:
import styled from 'styled-components';

const InputContainer = styled.div`
	padding: 0.8rem 0;
	display: flex;
	gap: 1rem;
`;

const Label = styled.label`
	font-size: 1rem;
	display: block;
	padding-left: 15px;
`;

const LabelHead = styled.label`
	font-weight: 2rem;
	line-height: 3rem;
`;

const Input = styled.input`
	height: 30px;
`;

const Checkbox = styled.input``;

const StyledForm = styled.form`
	display: flex;
	align-items: center;
	justify-content: center;
	font-size: 1.2rem;
	background-color: white;
	width: 100%;
`;

const CheckboxContainer = styled.div`
	display: flex;
	gap: 1rem;
`;

const InputGroup = styled.div`
	grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(20rem, 1fr));
`;

const CheckboxItem = styled.div`
	display: flex;
`;

const CheckboxGroup = styled.div`
	display: flex;
	flex-direction: column;
`;

function RecipeFilter() {
	return (
		<StyledForm>
			<CheckboxContainer>
				<CheckboxGroup>
					<LabelHead> Intolerances </LabelHead>

					<CheckboxItem>
						<Checkbox type='checkbox' />
						<Label>Dairy</Label>
					</CheckboxItem>

					<CheckboxItem>
						<Checkbox type='checkbox' />
						<Label>Gluten</Label>
					</CheckboxItem>

					<CheckboxItem>
						<Checkbox type='checkbox' />
						<Label>Peanut</Label>
					</CheckboxItem>

					<CheckboxItem>
						<Checkbox type='checkbox' />
						<Label>Sesame</Label>
					</CheckboxItem>

					<CheckboxItem>
						<Checkbox type='checkbox' />
						<Label>Seafood</Label>
					</CheckboxItem>

					<CheckboxItem>
						<Checkbox type='checkbox' />
						<Label>Shellfish</Label>
					</CheckboxItem>

					<CheckboxItem>
						<Checkbox type='checkbox' />
						<Label>Nuts</Label>
					</CheckboxItem>

					<CheckboxItem>
						<Checkbox type='checkbox' />
						<Label>Wheat</Label>
					</CheckboxItem>
				</CheckboxGroup>

				<CheckboxGroup>
					<LabelHead> Diets </LabelHead>
					<CheckboxItem>
						<Checkbox type='checkbox' />
						<Label>GlutenFree</Label>
					</CheckboxItem>

					<CheckboxItem>
						<Checkbox type='checkbox' />
						<Label>Ketogenic </Label>
					</CheckboxItem>

					<CheckboxItem>
						<Checkbox type='checkbox' />
						<Label>Vegetarian </Label>
					</CheckboxItem>

					<CheckboxItem>
						<Checkbox type='checkbox' />
						<Label>LactoVegetarian </Label>
					</CheckboxItem>

					<CheckboxItem>
						<Checkbox type='checkbox' />
						<Label>OvoVegetarian </Label>
					</CheckboxItem>

					<CheckboxItem>
						<Checkbox type='checkbox' />
						<Label>Vegan</Label>
					</CheckboxItem>

					<CheckboxItem>
						<Checkbox type='checkbox' />
						<Label>Pescatarian</Label>
					</CheckboxItem>

					<CheckboxItem>
						<Checkbox type='checkbox' />
						<Label>Paleo</Label>
					</CheckboxItem>

					<CheckboxItem>
						<Checkbox type='checkbox' />
						<Label>Primal</Label>
					</CheckboxItem>

					<CheckboxItem>
						<Checkbox type='checkbox' />
						<Label>LowFODMAP</Label>
					</CheckboxItem>

					<CheckboxItem>
						<Checkbox type='checkbox' />
						<Label>Whole30 </Label>
					</CheckboxItem>
				</CheckboxGroup>
			</CheckboxContainer>

			<InputGroup>
				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='minCal'> Min Calories </Label>
					<Input type='number' name='minCal' />
				</InputContainer>

				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='maxCal'> Max Calories </Label>
					<Input type='number' name='maxCal' />
				</InputContainer>

				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='minCarbs'> Min Carbs </Label>
					<Input type='number' name='minCarbs' />
				</InputContainer>

				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='maxCarbs'> Max Carbs </Label>
					<Input type='number' name='maxCarbs' />
				</InputContainer>

				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='minProtein'> Min Protein </Label>
					<Input type='number' name='minProtein' />
				</InputContainer>

				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='maxProtein'> Max Protein </Label>
					<Input type='number' name='maxProtein' />
				</InputContainer>

				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='minSugar'> Min Sugar </Label>
					<Input type='number' name='minSugar' />
				</InputContainer>

				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='maxSugar'> Max Sugar </Label>
					<Input type='number' name='maxSugar' />
				</InputContainer>

				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='minSodium'> Min Sodium </Label>
					<Input type='number' name='minSodium' />
				</InputContainer>

				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='maxSodium'> Max Sodium </Label>
					<Input type='number' name='maxSodium' />
				</InputContainer>

				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='minSatFat'> Min Saturated Fat </Label>
					<Input type='number' name='minSatFat' />
				</InputContainer>

				<InputContainer>
					<Label for='maxSatFat'> Max Saturated Fat</Label>
					<Input type='number' name='maxSatFat' />
				</InputContainer>
			</InputGroup>
		</StyledForm>
	);
}

export default RecipeFilter;
